amic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/143700/', '[1] "Product Information. Zydelig (idelalisib)." Gilead Sciences, Foster City, CA.[2] "Product Information. Hivid (zalcitabine)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.', 1767363024);
